  <h2>How I Think About This Business</h2>
  <p>My core belief is that being a good person will produce a greater ROI than any strategy. That sounds simple, but it's actually a pretty different way to run a real estate business.</p>
  <p>A lot of cash buyers show up with lowball offers and high-pressure tactics — create urgency, get a signature before the seller thinks too hard. I take the opposite approach. Show up honestly, explain the offer, answer every question, and let you decide on your own timeline.</p>
  <p>If my number doesn't work for you — no hard feelings. If you want to think about it for a week — that's fine. If you want me to explain exactly how I arrived at the offer — I'll walk you through it.</p>

  <h2>What You Can Expect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>A real conversation — not a sales pitch</li>
    <li>A fair offer based on actual market data</li>
    <li>Straight answers even if they're not what you hoped to hear</li>
    <li>A smooth, professional closing with a local title company</li>
    <li>No pressure to decide quickly</li>
    <li>Zero fees, zero commissions, zero surprises</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>The Areas I Buy In</h2>
  <p>I buy houses throughout Wichita and all surrounding Sedgwick County communities — Derby, Haysville, Andover, Mulvane, Augusta, El Dorado, Park City, Bel Aire, Valley Center, Goddard, Maize, and more.</p>
  <p>If you're not sure whether your area qualifies, just call. If it's outside my range, I'll tell you upfront.</p>

